nity, not just to make money, but to break down barriers. Risking a backlash from white conservatives, he built an all-black team of sales representatives who traveled across the country, often riding on segregated trains or in private cars that shielded them from harassment.<\/span>","time":1492285436,"resto":121247651,"id":"d\/5cKpuo","country":"US","country_name":"United States"}]}